# Hauswert-Franken

Professionelle Website für Hauswert-Franken - Hochwertige Sanierung, Modernisierung und Innenausbau in Franken.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Next.js 15 (App Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Package Manager**: Bun

## Features

- **Corporate Luxury Design**: Elegant, professional design suitable for a premium renovation company
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first design that works on all devices
- **SEO Optimized**: Dynamic pages for cities and services, structured data, sitemap
- **Performance**: Optimized for PageSpeed scores
- **Contact Form**: Detailed lead qualification form with image upload and compression
- **Analytics Ready**: Event tracking for conversions

## Pages

- `/` - Homepage
- `/leistungen` - Services overview
- `/leistung/[service]` - Individual service pages
- `/projekte` - Projects/References
- `/ueber-uns` - About page
- `/kontakt` - Contact page with detailed form
- `/thank-you` - Thank you page (conversion tracking)
- `/[city]` - City-specific landing pages
- `/[city]/[service]` - City + Service combination pages
- `/impressum` - Legal information
- `/datenschutz` - Privacy policy

## SEO

The website generates thousands of SEO-optimized pages:
- 160+ cities in Franken region
- 12 service categories
- City × Service combinations

## Development

```bash
# Install dependencies
bun install

# Start development server
bun run dev

# Build for production
bun run build

# Start production server
bun run start
```

## Structure

```
src/
├── app/                    # Next.js App Router pages
│   ├── [citySlug]/        # Dynamic city pages
│   ├── leistung/          # Service pages
│   └── ...
├── components/
│   ├── layout/            # Header, Footer
│   ├── sections/          # Page sections
│   └── ui/                # shadcn/ui components
└── lib/
    ├── data/              # Cities and services data
    └── utils/             # Analytics, image compression
```

## Contact

- **Company**: Hauswert-Franken
- **Region**: Franken (Nürnberg + 100km radius)
- **Services**: Sanierung, Modernisierung, Innenausbau
